span class="_ _8"></span>肯定会什</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf6 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">么都不想，<span class="_ _a"></span>放下一切去救她。<span class="_ _a"></span>同样，<span class="_ _a"></span>世间上的任何一个众生，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf7 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">前世都当过我们母亲，<span class="_ _8"></span>她们如今没有智慧的双目，<span class="_ _8"></span>没有善知</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ydd ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">识的引导，<span class="_ _6"></span>无明愚痴、<span class="_ _9"></span>疯狂颠倒，<span class="_ _6"></span>在轮回的悬崖边，<span class="_ _9"></span>随时都</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yde ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">有堕入恶趣深渊的危险，<span class="_ _8"></span>如果我不去救，<span class="_ _8"></span>那谁去救呢？倘若</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
